%p Hello #{@name},
%p We are sorry to inform you that your order for today is cancelled.
%p You can place your order again.
%p The time window has been extended to #{TIME_EXTENTION.minutes.from_now.strftime('%I:%M%p')}.
%b Recommended Vendors:
%table{ style: 'cellspacing: 20px cellpadding: 20px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #ddd;' }
  %tr
    %th{style: 'padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd;'}Vendor
    %th{style: 'padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd;'}Minimum order
    - @terminals.each do |terminal|
      %tr
        %td{style: 'padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;'}
          =image_tag terminal.logo_url, width: 80, height: 80
          %div{style: 'font-weight: bold'}#{terminal.name}
        %td{style: 'padding: 20px;  border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold'}
          â‚¹ #{terminal.min_order_amount}
          %p= link_to 'Place Order', new_terminal_order_url(terminal.id), style: 'background-color: DodgerBlue; color: white; font-size: 10px; padding: 10px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;'
%p Place your order by signing in: 
%p= link_to 'Sign In',  new_user_session_url, style: 'background-color: #4CAF50; color: white;font-size: 10px; padding: 10px; margin: 4px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 15px;'
%p Have a great day!!!
%p Regards,
%p The hunger terminal team!
